beer.beer_description:
Refreshingly bold and perfectly balanced, Prima has set the gold standard for pilsners since 1996 with its German and Czech Noble hops and German malt. 

Loads of earthy, herbal noble hop character with subtle malt complexity in the aroma. Flavor is very hop forward with ample bitterness. Balanced malt and clean fermentation.
